net.antidot.paf

Interface Configuration


  • public interface Configuration
    The configuration object responsible of the configuration of the filter. In classical PaF execution, an instance represents the "paf.xml" file.
    Version:
    7.4
    Author:
    Laurent Mazuel

      • get_input_type

        LayerType.Type get_input_type(LayerType.Type default_type)
        Get the predefined parameter "input_layer" as a layer type.
        Parameters:
        default_type - The default type if param is not defined.
        Returns:
        The input layer type, parameter "input_layer" or the given "default_type" if not defined.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - If "input_layer" is not a layer type.
